&lt;li&gt;Expertise in one or more of the following:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;REST and GraphQL APIs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;API lifecycle management tools (e.g., Postman, Swagger/OpenAPI, Kong, Apigee)&lt;/li&gt;
